data.description: Welcome to the enchanting Mediterranean home in the Bellalago community, where modern elegance meets tranquil living. This impressive 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence boasts an inviting contemporary design, offering comfort and style.    Step inside to discover the spacious interior, highlighted by an enclosed patio spanning an impressive 20x50 feet, providing the perfect space for relaxation and entertainment. The patio's strategic placement allows you to relish breathtaking water views, creating a soothing backdrop that will captivate your senses.    Nestled on a coveted corner lot, this home offers a sense of privacy and extra outdoor space for you to savor. And with the added security of being within a man-gated community, you can enjoy peace of mind and a serene atmosphere.    Seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor living, this Mediterranean gem presents a remarkable opportunity for those seeking a harmonious lifestyle. Whether you're hosting gatherings with loved ones or simply enjoying the tranquil surroundings, this residence is the epitome of refined living.    Don't miss out on this great opportunity to own a slice of Mediterranean paradise in the sought-after Bellalago community. Experience the allure of modern design, stunning water views, and a secure, gated haven—a true sanctuary to call your own.
